snippet.title: Hiveversary Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Hive Time is a cute and zany hive builder, updated for its very first birthday with some new events, some new music, some new hats, chat integration, and many other improvements/fixes. Available now for Linux, MacOS (version 10.14 or lower) and Windows!

Website: http://hivetime.twolofbees.com/

Itch.io: https://cheeseness.itch.io/hive-time

Twitter: https://twitter.com/hive_time/

Bandcamp: https://kestrelpi.bandcamp.com/album/hive-time

RedBubble: https://www.redbubble.com/people/cheeseness/shop?artistUserName=cheeseness&collections=1936171&iaCode=all-departments&sortOrder=relevant
